	}

		}

							set_variable = { 
								which = ayv
								which = ayp
							}
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									AND = { 
										check_variable = { 
											which = ayv
											value = 0.001
										}
									}
								}
								divide_variable = { 
									which = ayv
									which = aaz
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = ayv
									value = 100
								}
							}
						}
						else_if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = { 
										which = aef
										value = 3
									}
								}
							}
							change_variable = { 
								which = axe
								which = kdu
							}
							change_variable = { 
								which = axf
								which = kdv
							}
							change_variable = { 
								which = axg
								which = kdw
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = aer
								which = axe
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = aes
								which = axf
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = aeg
								which = axg
							}
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									OR = { 
										AND = { 
											is_variable_equal = { 
												which = aaw
												value = 0
											}
										}
										AND = { 
											is_variable_equal = { 
												which = aer
												value = 0.001
											}
										}
									}
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = aer
									value = 0
								}
							}
							else = { 
								divide_variable = { 
									which = aer
									which = aaw
								}
							}
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									OR = { 
										AND = { 
											is_variable_equal = { 
												which = aax
												value = 0
											}
										}
										AND = { 
											is_variable_equal = { 
												which = aes
												value = 0.001
											}
										}
									}
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = aes
									value = 0
								}
							}
							else = { 
								divide_variable = { 
									which = aes
									which = aax
								}
							}
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									OR = { 
										AND = { 
											is_variable_equal = { 
												which = aay
												value = 0
											}
										}
										AND = { 
											is_variable_equal = { 
												which = aeg
												value = 0.001
											}
										}
									}
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = aeg
									value = 0
								}
							}
							else = { 
								divide_variable = { 
									which = aeg
									which = aay
								}
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = axw
								which = aer
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = axx
								which = aes
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = axy
								which = aeg
							}
							multiply_variable = { 
								which = axw
								value = 100
							}
							multiply_variable = { 
								which = axx
								value = 100
							}
							multiply_variable = { 
								which = axy
								value = 100
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = ayq
								which = axe
							}
							change_variable = { 
								which = ayq
								which = axf
							}
							change_variable = { 
								which = ayq
								which = axg
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = ayw
								which = ayq
							}
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									AND = { 
										check_variable = { 
											which = ayw
											value = 0.001
										}
									}
								}
								divide_variable = { 
									which = ayw
									which = aaz
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = ayw
									value = 100
								}
							}
						}
						set_province_flag = DG_Update
						set_variable = { 
							which = kdu
							value = 0
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = kdv
							value = 0
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = kdw
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = qac
						value = 0
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = adv
									value = 3
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = azz
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = adx
									value = 3
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = baa
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = adz
									value = 3
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = bab
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = aeb
									value = 3
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = bac
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = aed
									value = 3
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = {

							value = 100

					else_if = {

								}
							}

	option = { 
		name = "OPT.ISEE"
		trigger = { 
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = reformed_presence
			}
		}
	}
	after = { 
		owner = { 
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						has_country_flag = reformed_presence
					}
				}
				hidden_effect = { 
					country_event = { 
						id = DG_Reformed.002
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Reformed.118
	title = "DG_Reformed.118.title"
	desc = "DG_Reformed.118.desc"
	picture = ANGLICAN_SERMON_eventPicture
	trigger = { 
		is_religion_enabled = reformed
		has_province_flag = printing_press_p
		owner = { 
			reform_desire = 1.00
		}
		NOT = { 
			religion_years = { 
				reformed = 50
			}
		}
		AND = { 
			continent = europe
			religion = reformed
			NOT = { 
				province_id = 2530
			}
			is_reformation_center = no
			is_island = no
			expelling_minorities = no
			development = 10
			NOT = { 
				Academia = 100
			}
			NOT = { 
				current_age = age_of_revolutions
			}
			NOT = { 
				calc_true_if = { 
					all_province = { 
						continent = europe
						religion = ROOT
						is_reformation_center = yes
					}
					amount = 3
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				any_neighbor_province = { 
					is_reformation_center = yes
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				any_province = { 
					superregion = PREV
					is_reformation_center = yes
					religion = reformed
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = tropical
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = arid
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = arctic
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = arctic
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = taiga
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = tundra
			}
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 5
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.5
			has_province_flag = ref_craddle
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.95
			culture_group = langue_d_oc
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.75
			culture_group = low_frankish
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 2.00
			culture_group = langue_d_oil
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 2.50
			superregion = italy_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 2.50
			superregion = iberia_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.25
			superregion = germany_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 2.70
			superregion = greater_austrian_circle_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 2.00
			superregion = balkan_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.80
			superregion = commonwealth_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.25
			superregion = scandinavian_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 5.0
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = accept_03
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 10.0
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = silence_03
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.GOOD"
		trigger = { 
			owner = { 
				religion = reformed
			}
		}
		add_reform_center = reformed
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_province_modifier = religious_enthusiasm
			}
			extend_province_modifier = { 
				name = religious_enthusiasm
				duration = 3650
			}
		}
		else = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = religious_enthusiasm
				duration = 3650
				hidden = yes
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.DAMN"
		trigger = { 
			owner = { 
				NOT = { 
					religion = reformed
				}
			}
		}
		add_reform_center = reformed
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_province_modifier = heretic_centre
			}
			extend_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_centre
				duration = 3650
			}
		}
		else = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_centre
				duration = 3650
				hidden = yes
			}
		}
	}
}
province_event = { 
	id = DG_Reformed.119
	title = "DG_Reformed.119.title"
	desc = "DG_Reformed.119.desc"
	picture = ANGLICAN_SERMON_eventPicture
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		months = 1
	}
	trigger = { 
		religion = reformed
		is_reformation_center = yes
		Academia = 100
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.NOTED"
		remove_reform_center = reformed
	}
}
province_event = { 
	id = DG_Reformed.201
	title = "DG_Reformed.201.title"
	desc = "DG_Reformed.201.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	hidden = yes
	trigger = { 
		is_religion_enabled = reformed
		owner = { 
			NOT = { 
				religion = reformed
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			AND = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adv
						value = 3
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = jwg
						value = 1
					}
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adx
						value = 3
					}
				}
				AND = {

						which = jwh
						value = 1
					}
				}
			}

						which = adz
						value = 3
					}
				}
				AND = {

						which = jwi
						value = 1
					}
				}
			}

					}
				}
				AND = {

				}
			}

						value = 3
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = jwl
						value = 1
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 20
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.20
			OR = { 
				AND = { 
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = adv
							value = 3
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = jxd
							value = 0.1
						}
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = adx
							value = 3
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = jxe
							value = 0.1
						}
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = adz
							value = 3
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = jxf

					}
				}
				AND = {

						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = aeb
							value = 3
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = jxg
							value = 0.1
						}
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = aed
							value = 3
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = jxh
							value = 0.1
						}
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = aef
							value = 3
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = jxi
							value = 0.1
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.EXCELLENT"
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adv
						value = 3
					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = jwg
				value = -1
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adx
						value = 3
					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = jwh
				value = -1
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adz
						value = 3
					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = jwi
				value = -1
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = aeb
						value = 3
					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = jwj
				value = -1
			}
		}
		else_if = {

					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = {

			}
		}

						which = aef
						value = 3
					}
				}

			change_variable = {

				id = DG_Reformed.202
			}

				}

				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = aeb
						value = 3
					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = azw
				value = -2
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = aed
						value = 3
					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = azx
				value = -2
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = aef
						value = 3
					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = azy
				value = -2
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				owner = { 
					has_country_flag = ref_inquis_info
				}
			}
			province_event = { 
				id = DG_Reformed.206
			}
		}
	}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Reformed.302
	title = "DG_Reformed.301.title"
	desc = "DG_Reformed.301.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.OHNO"
		trigger_switch = { 
			on_trigger = has_province_flag
			mn_trauma_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_10_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_20 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_20_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_30 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_30_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_40 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_40_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_50 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_50_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_60 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_60_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_70 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_70_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_80 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_80_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_90 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_90_tt
			}
		}
	}
	after = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_20
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_30
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_40
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_50
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_60
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_70
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_80
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_90
		}
	}
}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Reformed.312
	title = "DG_Reformed.311.title"
	desc = "DG_Reformed.311.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.OHNO"
		trigger_switch = { 
			on_trigger = has_province_flag
			mn_unrest_min_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_min_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_min_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_min_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_min_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_min_3_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_low_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_low_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_low_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_low_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_low_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_low_3_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_mid_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_mid_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_mid_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_mid_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_mid_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_mid_3_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_imp_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_imp_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_imp_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_imp_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_imp_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_imp_3_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_max_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_max_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_max_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_max_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_max_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_max_3_tt
			}
		}
	}
	after = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_min_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_min_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_min_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_low_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_low_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_low_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_mid_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_mid_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_mid_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_imp_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_imp_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_imp_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_10
		}
	}
